00:33:18,018 --> 00:33:19,724
(Weather turns warmer, )

770
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:23,105
(and the plants sprout.)

771
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,202
(Clear scenery and weather, )

772
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:29,286
(all things are revitalized.)

