00:33:46,057 --> 00:33:47,057
Tian Zhen.

776
00:33:55,498 --> 00:33:56,498
Nephew.

777
00:33:57,097 --> 00:33:58,097
Nephew!

778
00:33:59,658 --> 00:34:00,658
Your wife...

779
00:34:01,297 --> 00:34:03,775
She tied a red knot behind every tree.

780
00:34:03,858 --> 00:34:06,134
What kind of ritual is that?

781
00:34:06,217 --> 00:34:07,815
Are you going to summon

782
00:34:07,898 --> 00:34:08,656
all the lost souls here?

783
00:34:08,739 --> 00:34:10,134
It feels inauspicious to me.

784
00:34:10,217 --> 00:34:11,657
Guys, listen up.

785
00:34:12,578 --> 00:34:15,738
There are many forked paths
in this mountain.

786
00:34:16,617 --> 00:34:18,175
When we're descending the mountain,

787
00:34:18,258 --> 00:34:19,455
if you get separated from the group,

788
00:34:19,538 --> 00:34:21,498
just follow the red knots down

789
00:34:22,137 --> 00:34:23,255
and you'll be fine.

790
00:34:23,338 --> 00:34:25,655
Please don't get separated.

791
00:34:25,738 --> 00:34:28,374
There are wolves, bears,

792
00:34:28,457 --> 00:34:29,657
and boars here.

793
00:34:30,137 --> 00:34:31,697
You guys must be careful.

794
00:34:31,990 --> 00:34:34,034
-Alright.
-Are you trying to deceive a kid here?

795
