I'm sure this path is frequently used.

796
00:34:35,778 --> 00:34:37,495
How could there be wolves, bears,

797
00:34:37,578 --> 00:34:38,897
or wild beasts here?

798
00:34:39,818 --> 00:34:40,656
There weren't any in the past.

799
00:34:40,739 --> 00:34:41,857
But now,

800
00:34:42,098 --> 00:34:43,538
it's been over two decades.

801
00:34:43,818 --> 00:34:45,334
The local youngsters

802
00:34:45,417 --> 00:34:46,935
had moved to the city
in search of better jobs.

803
00:34:47,018 --> 00:34:49,895
Their parents are old now.

804
00:34:49,978 --> 00:34:51,457
Some of them have passed away too.

805
00:34:51,897 --> 00:34:53,695
Therefore, some of the houses here

806
00:34:53,778 --> 00:34:54,774
are abandoned.

807
00:34:54,857 --> 00:34:55,696
That's how this forest

808
00:34:55,779 --> 00:34:57,578
grew gradually.

809
00:34:58,217 --> 00:34:59,217
And that's why

810
00:34:59,657 --> 00:35:01,266
there are wild beasts lurking around.

811
00:35:01,377 --> 00:35:02,377
Come on, let's go.

812
00:35:13,578 --> 00:35:14,578
Ling Ian.

813
00:35:15,137 --> 00:35:16,137
Coming.

814
00:35:22,298 --> 00:35:24,334
I thought animal dungs
were natural fertilizers?

815
00:35:24,417 --> 00:35:25,455
Why are you picking them up?

816
00:35:25,538 --> 00:35:26,578
This is a type of herb.

817
00:35:27,137 --> 00:35:28,137
A type of herb?

818
00:35:29,298 --> 00:35:30,735
Guys, look.

819
00:35:30,818 --> 00:35:32,935
Have you guys tried doing
any pharmacological experiments?

820
00:35:33,018 --> 00:35:34,015
When I was in college,

821
00:35:34,098 --> 00:35:36,018
I studied basic TCM theories.

822
00:35:36,177 --> 00:35:38,255
I know that bat dung
is good for the eyes.

823
00:35:38,338 --> 00:35:39,814
It's known as Faeces Vespertilionum.

824
00:35:39,897 --> 00:35:41,058
But I'm perplexed.

825
00:35:41,258 --> 00:35:42,735
Bats consume different food every day.

826
00:35:42,818 --> 00:35:43,774
They produce different dung every day.

