00:35:43,857 --> 00:35:45,655
How could you guys know which bat dung

828
00:35:45,738 --> 00:35:46,857
could cure blindness?

829
00:35:47,457 --> 00:35:48,374
How do I put it?

830
00:35:48,457 --> 00:35:49,655
Don't you think it's too irresponsible

831
00:35:49,738 --> 00:35:50,574
for you guys to collect random dung

832
00:35:50,657 --> 00:35:51,818
for your patients?

833
00:35:52,538 --> 00:35:54,857
If so, the civet coffee you like so much,

834
00:35:55,498 --> 00:35:57,094
do you think they're the same

835
00:35:57,177 --> 00:35:58,177
if you test them?

836
00:35:58,818 --> 00:35:59,905
They're different, right?

837
00:36:00,417 --> 00:36:03,538
TCM practitioners aren't the only ones
utilizing animal dungs.

838
00:36:03,697 --> 00:36:05,895
You shouldn't belittle them.

839
00:36:05,978 --> 00:36:07,374
Everything exists

840
00:36:07,457 --> 00:36:10,098
for its own reason.

841
00:36:11,217 --> 00:36:12,738
Some animal dungs

842
00:36:13,018 --> 00:36:14,538
are worth more than gold.

843
00:36:14,738 --> 00:36:16,134
You guys can search for it online.

844
00:36:16,217 --> 00:36:18,897
This dung costs around
8,000 to 10,000 yuan

845
00:36:19,937 --> 00:36:21,498
per gram.

846
00:36:22,177 --> 00:36:23,177
What kind of animal?

847
00:36:23,538 --> 00:36:25,784
What kind of animal is that valuable?

848
00:36:25,937 --> 00:36:27,198
Their dung is that expensive?

849
00:36:27,897 --> 00:36:29,655
Tell me what kind of animal it is.
I'll go and keep one.

850
00:36:29,738 --> 00:36:31,255
After that, I'll wait for it to poop.

851
00:36:31,338 --> 00:36:32,599
I'll sell its dung for money.

852
00:36:33,217 --> 00:36:36,897
It's called a sperm whale.

853
00:36:37,498 --> 00:36:39,455
A sperm whale

854
00:36:39,538 --> 00:36:42,695
is around 50 tons heavy.

855
00:36:42,778 --> 00:36:44,083
Do you think you can keep one?

856
00:36:45,818 --> 00:36:46,818
You can't, right?

857
00:36:47,417 --> 00:36:49,617
A sperm whale's dung is called

858
00:36:49,897 --> 00:36:52,498
ambergris.

859
00:36:53,177 --> 00:36:54,975
We use it to make incense,

860
00:36:55,058 --> 00:36:56,534
perfumes,

861
00:36:56,617 --> 00:36:57,416
and so on.

862
00:36:57,499 --> 00:36:58,975
It's an amazing material.

863
00:36:59,058 --> 00:37:01,137
So, you guys mustn't look down
on animal dungs.

864
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:02,495
In Compendium of Materia Medica,

865
00:37:02,578 --> 00:37:04,574
there are many kinds

866
00:37:04,657 --> 00:37:05,897
of animal dungs

867
00:37:06,377 --> 00:37:07,551
that have TCM applications.

868
00:37:08,217 --> 00:37:11,657
Let's take Wulingzhi as an example.

869
00:37:11,897 --> 00:37:13,094
Even now, the field of TCM
is still using it.

870
00:37:13,177 --> 00:37:15,175
So, what's the similarity between

871
00:37:15,258 --> 00:37:16,345
TCM and Western medicine?

872
00:37:16,457 --> 00:37:19,457
Both fields hope that humans
can live healthily.

873
00:37:20,258 --> 00:37:21,258
If they're unhealthy,

874
00:37:22,018 --> 00:37:24,134
if we have to sustain their lives
with medicine and machines,

875
00:37:24,217 --> 00:37:25,614
that's not called longevity.

876
00:37:25,697 --> 00:37:27,058
That's

877
00:37:27,697 --> 00:37:29,258
torture.

878
00:37:30,498 --> 00:37:32,298
Nephew, where's the animal then?

879
00:37:32,578 --> 00:37:33,374
Where can I find one?

880
00:37:33,457 --> 00:37:34,455
In the sea.

881
00:37:34,538 --> 00:37:35,538
Let's go.

882
00:37:36,538 --> 00:37:38,780
How much is that dung worth?

883
00:38:23,738 --> 00:38:25,655
Say, although we're in the wilderness,

884
00:38:25,738 --> 00:38:26,854
people do come here often.

885
00:38:26,937 --> 00:38:29,655
Even the fruits here are fresh.

886
00:38:29,738 --> 00:38:30,738
Am I right, Nephew?

887
00:38:31,738 --> 00:38:32,937
Mr Huang Mei

888
00:38:33,498 --> 00:38:34,697
is a renowned figure.

889
00:38:35,457 --> 00:38:37,023
He's well-known throughout the land.

890
00:38:37,738 --> 00:38:39,695
Although he has passed away
for several decades,

891
00:38:39,778 --> 00:38:41,578
people still worship him.

892
00:38:44,018 --> 00:38:45,018
What?

893
00:38:45,338 --> 00:38:46,176
Come here.

894
00:38:46,259 --> 00:38:47,298
What are you doing?

895
00:38:47,498 --> 00:38:50,151
We'll worship our predecessors soon.
Your attire must be tidy.

896
00:38:50,258 --> 00:38:51,258
Come here.

897
00:38:54,498 --> 00:38:55,335
My attire is tidy.

898
00:38:55,418 --> 00:38:57,417
I'm wearing extra pants.

899
00:38:59,457 --> 00:39:00,457
Button up.

900
00:39:05,818 --> 00:39:06,818
Tou Tou,

901
00:39:07,338 --> 00:39:08,978
observe closely.

902
00:39:10,018 --> 00:39:12,584
You're the successor of
the Jiang family's acupuncture sect.

903
00:39:13,018 --> 00:39:14,415
You'll be the one leading the sect

904
00:39:14,498 --> 00:39:17,217
and the younger generations to worship

905
00:39:17,538 --> 00:39:19,978
our predecessors in the future.

906
00:39:22,578 --> 00:39:23,534
Guys,

907
00:39:23,617 --> 00:39:25,455
since today is Qingming Festival...

908
00:39:25,538 --> 00:39:26,818
We'll take a day off then.

909
00:39:35,098 --> 00:39:37,377
Qingming Festival is one of
the 24 Solar Terms.

910
00:39:39,018 --> 00:39:40,215
According to
Yellow Emperor's Inner Classic,

911
00:39:40,298 --> 00:39:42,857
humans are connected to Heaven and Earth.

912
00:39:43,978 --> 00:39:45,065
If so, those who are sick

913
00:39:46,018 --> 00:39:48,255
are not in sync with Heaven and Earth.

914
00:39:48,338 --> 00:39:50,255
If so, what do we examine
if we're TCM practitioners?

915
00:39:50,338 --> 00:39:53,134
We examine the person who is sick,

916
00:39:53,217 --> 00:39:55,098
not the disease they have.

917
00:39:56,258 --> 00:39:58,738
We need to make people
in sync with Heaven and Earth.

918
00:39:58,937 --> 00:40:01,217
We need to let them know
the change of the seasons

919
00:40:01,498 --> 00:40:02,978
and where their hearts belong.

920
00:40:03,217 --> 00:40:05,391
That way, they won't deviate
from the central path.

921
00:40:05,498 --> 00:40:06,455
Second,

922
00:40:06,538 --> 00:40:09,897
Qingming Festival is an important time
for us to worship our predecessors.

923
00:40:10,018 --> 00:40:11,578
If so, I hope

924
00:40:12,417 --> 00:40:13,697
that everyone

925
00:40:14,018 --> 00:40:17,298
can worship our predecessors
with sincerity.

926
00:40:30,217 --> 00:40:31,457
Tou Tou, bow.

927
00:40:33,098 --> 00:40:34,175
I don't know them.

928
00:40:34,258 --> 00:40:35,294
And, they're not your relatives.

929
00:40:35,377 --> 00:40:36,377
I think

930
00:40:36,738 --> 00:40:38,818
this is ridiculous.

931
00:40:39,697 --> 00:40:41,098
This is so strange.

932
00:40:48,018 --> 00:40:49,778
Let us read

933
00:40:50,937 --> 00:40:52,854
Virtue of A Great Physician
in front of Mr Huang's grave

934
00:40:52,937 --> 00:40:54,217
to comfort our predecessors.

935
00:40:54,457 --> 00:40:56,975
May we have successors and
our initial goals be unchanged.

936
00:40:57,058 --> 00:40:58,334
Healing the wounded and
rescuing the dying

937
00:40:58,417 --> 00:40:59,657
are my ambitions.

938
00:41:00,657 --> 00:41:02,215
Virtue of A Great Physician.

939
00:41:02,298 --> 00:41:03,415
Even if you read it,

940
00:41:03,498 --> 00:41:04,818
do you think he can hear it?

941
00:41:05,818 --> 00:41:07,134
Even if we read together,

942
00:41:07,217 --> 00:41:09,457
can he hear us?

943
00:41:10,697 --> 00:41:11,697
He can't, right?

944
00:41:15,864 --> 00:41:17,237
(The prescriptions and remedies
used in this drama)

945
00:41:17,320 --> 00:41:18,357
(are referenced from relevant
traditional Chinese medicine books)

946
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:20,745
(Do not use without medical advice)
